attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling a piece of furniture. They start by inspecting the base frame and assembling it. Then, they attach the legs to the frame and attach the tray. Next, they screw the tray with brackets and place the second tray. Finally, they screw the third bracket on the top of the drawer and rotate the furniture regularly.
